products.name: CAYDEN CAMPAIGN 4-DOOR GLASS SIDEBOARD & HUTCH
products.deskripsi: European campaign furnishings of the 19th century inspired our collection by the Van Thiels, echoed in the simple strength of the shapes, the rustic grain of the solid oak and the hand-cast metal hardware with corner brackets that accent each piece. Subtle details including tapered legs and concealed hinges lend refinement to the clean, forthright silhouettes.
